00:00:12.571 --> 00:00:17.246
We're observing conduction, conduction,

00:00:17.246 --> 00:00:21.789
convection, convection,

00:00:21.789 --> 00:00:24.268
convection,

00:00:24.268 --> 00:00:27.968
