00:00:27.968 --> 00:00:32.870
So I'll do this, thermal, thermal radiation,

00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:35.999
thermal radiation.

00:00:35.999 --> 00:00:37.218
And I could say thermal conduction,

00:00:37.218 --> 00:00:39.616
thermal convection, and thermal radiation,

00:00:39.616 --> 00:00:41.281
