00:03:13.090 --> 00:03:16.443
it's gonna fall around it, or try to go under it,

00:03:16.443 --> 00:03:17.784
because it is more dense,

00:03:17.784 --> 00:03:21.359
and then the less dense area is going to rise.

00:03:21.359 --> 00:03:22.436
And by doing that,

00:03:22.436 --> 00:03:27.415
you have the hotter molecules are moving upwards

00:03:27.415 --> 00:03:29.973
